text: Edeltraud Schramm (16 December 1923 - 1 October 2002) was an Austrian gymnast. She competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:2002 deaths Category:Austrian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Linz
